    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several minor scuffs, a few small door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear and some light staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though the next owner should expect to perform some routine maintenance, such as replacing the brake pads and addressing a slow leak in the power steering fluid, in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
