      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs like a dream and is ready to hit the road for some new adventures! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
