    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its signature balance with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing the primary structural concerns of this platform. The throttle response is sharp, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback enthusiasts demand. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a driven machine, the drivetrain remains robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Runs well. No major issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
